Limitations
--------------
The script relies on ICMP (Ping) responses.
A server may appear unreachable due to network issues rather than an actual shutdown.
Firewall restrictions may affect results.
Additional validation methods (WinRM, VMware status, Hyper-V status, etc.) may be required in highly restricted environments.


Recommended Workflow
----------------------
This script is intended to be used immediately after running the PS Server Bulk Shutdown Script.
Workflow Example

Execute bulk shutdown script.
Allow sufficient time for servers to power down.
Launch the shutdown verification script.
Confirm powered-off systems.
Investigate any remaining online servers.


